topics.string:
Here is a template that you can use for building your own Help topics (Note that 'help' does not need to be added to the start of 'pattern'):

{
    "topics" : [
        {
            "pattern" : "\b(some topic)\b",
            "title" : "Some Topic",
            "string" : "
Topic content here...
",
            "links" : [
                "help related topic",
                "help another topic"
            ]
        }
    ]
}
